The paper deals with deep neural networks and their application to object recognition tasks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of ridge regression and other DNN constituents also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the use of spectral histogram features may indicate a connection to signal processing (cs.NE) or multimedia (cs.MM).
